## [2026-03-07] session-1
**Decision**: Use claude-sonnet-4-6 for debate turns, claude-haiku-4-5-20251001 for summaries
**Why**: Sonnet for quality debate reasoning; Haiku for cheap rolling summaries between rounds
**Alternatives rejected**: All-Sonnet (too expensive for summaries), all-Haiku (quality too low for debate)
