## [2026-03-07] session-1
**Decision**: Start with Phase 1 spec implementation only (no Phase 2 features)
**Why**: Get working v1 first; Phase 2 (Annals, Forge, Barracks, Tribune) is out of scope for v1 per spec
**Alternatives rejected**: Building Phase 2 alongside (too much scope creep)
---

## [2026-03-07] session-1
**Decision**: Use Anthropic.SDK NuGet package (official) for Claude API calls
**Why**: Official SDK, well-maintained, supports streaming
**Alternatives rejected**: Raw HttpClient (more work, less reliable)
